---
description: CephasOps architecture review before coding
alwaysApply: true
---

Before writing or modifying code, perform an architecture safety review.

Return:

1. Feature summary
2. Tenant ownership (tenant or platform)
3. Required TenantScopeExecutor method
4. Guards affected
5. Potential risks

Do not write code until the review is complete.

Key platform rules:

Tenant-owned work → RunWithTenantScopeAsync(companyId)

Platform-wide work → RunWithPlatformBypassAsync()

Nullable-company path → RunWithTenantScopeOrBypassAsync() ONLY when justified.

Never weaken:

TenantSafetyGuard  
SiWorkflowGuard  
FinancialIsolationGuard  
EventStoreConsistencyGuard
